question.title: Problem with ProGuard and RoboGuice with @Inject annotations

node.contents: I'm having some problems with proguard when optimizing my android app. It seems that there is something done to an annotation class (@com.google.inject.Inject) which Dalvik/Harmony is not happy with at runtime.
